"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_I_1-10_ori","input":"还有因为我是个外国人，所以他每次帮我助我了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_I_1-10_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_I_1-11_ori","input":"我们真的是一个幸福的一对了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_I_1-11_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_I_1-12_ori","input":"有一天，他给我介绍一个他的堂妹了，然后那个堂妹真的喜欢我了，所以她给家人告诉了我真的是一个真的好女孩儿。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_I_1-12_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_I_1-18_ori","input":"他不是见我一个人，见了很多女人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_I_1-18_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_I_1-4_ori","input":"虽然他的年龄比我小俩岁，但看起来好像个成熟的男人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_I_1-4_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_I_1-8_ori","input":"然后他给我表白了，我们成为情侣了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_I_1-8_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_J_1-7_ori","input":"我忙跑上前去帮他盖上了井盖。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_J_1-7_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_K_1-4_ori","input":"对我来说世界上最伤心的事情是我看到别人失去他们的梦想，有一次我在看电视的时候，我看到一个球员讲他的悲剧，以前他算世界上最好的球员之一，可是有一天他和他的哥们去玩儿的时候，他们玩得很开心，喝着喝着就喝醉了，然后他开车要回家，突然在路上他不小心被卡车撞上了，结果他变成了残疾人，在转瞬间他的最宝贵的梦想就消失了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_K_1-4_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_L_1-10_ori","input":"时光很快快过两个月了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_L_1-10_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_L_1-15_ori","input":"那时我的心情是这样的：“天池不是令我流了很多眼泪的那个池吗？","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_L_1-15_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_L_1-19_ori","input":"这是件我最难忘的事。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_L_1-19_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_L_1-1_ori","input":"对我来说最难忘记的事就是有关天池和找对象的事情。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_L_1-1_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_L_1-3_ori","input":"两个月以后我忽然决定去新疆旅游。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_L_1-3_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_M_1-23_ori","input":"为了忘记她，我很快找到了新的女朋友。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_M_1-23_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_M_1-24_ori","input":"可是和她在一起两个月后，我发现我仍然不能忘记第一个女朋友，所以我给她说了实话，于是我们分手了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_M_1-24_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_M_1-31_ori","input":"辛亏我遇到她，否则我不会了解爱情的意义，我来中国学习汉语便很快忘记了她，可是我很怕以后爱上别的女孩子，因为分手的感觉很难过，我不想再来一次。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_M_1-31_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_O_1-14_ori","input":"在我爬山的时候，迎来了一阵风暴并开始下雨，又冷又累。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_O_1-14_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_O_1-4_ori","input":"名古屋是一个非常棒的城市，这里有很多美食。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_O_1-4_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_P_1-6_ori","input":"另外和我以前想象完全不一的是中国的饮食非常符合我的味口。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_P_1-6_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_Y_1-11_ori","input":"老人的早晨从6点开始。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_Y_1-11_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_Y_1-15_ori","input":"老人们每天都互相分享他们的小快乐！","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_Y_1-15_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1/CFL_Z_1-16_ori","input":"今年9月初我再次去北京的时候让我惊讶的情景就是市内到处有很多公共自行车了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Chinese-CFL/ad71b068e4581343dab897ef2d54abf102580897/zh_cfl-ud-test.conllu","source_case_id":"CFL_Z_1-16_ori","split":"test"},"source_id":"ud-chinese-cfl-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"ud-chinese-